    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐライブの始まる時間ですね……\nうまく出来るかな……",
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば昨日は夜遅くまで\n三人で新しい振り付けを練習してたんだよな？",
      "startTime": 14.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですけど、なんだか集中出来なくて\n同じところで何度も失敗しちゃって……",
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも本番ではちゃんとやりますから！\n大丈夫です！",
      "startTime": 29.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（クリスマスパーティーが中止になったことを）\n（まだ気にしてるみたいだな）",
      "startTime": 33.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん、ちょっと来てくれないか",
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でもライブが始まっちゃいますよ",
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.6666667,
          "startTime": 43.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.6666667,
          "startTime": 43.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンに見つからないように、気をつけて見てくれ",
      "startTime": 44.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "凄い人の数……\nこれ全部、ライブを観に来てくれた人達なんですか？",
      "startTime": 51.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "急なイベントで告知もろくに出来なかったのに\nこんなに大勢集まってくれるなんて……",
      "startTime": 60.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいる人達はみんな、クリスマスを\nトリエルと過ごしたくて集まってくれたんだ",
      "startTime": 66.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに沢山の人達が\n私達のライブを楽しみにしてくれていたんですね",
      "startTime": 71.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに私ときたら\nいつまでも気にして、うじうじ悩んで……",
      "startTime": 78.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "もっとしっかりしなきゃいけないのに、全然ダメですね",
      "startTime": 81.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "昨日も{user}さんに\n不満をぶつけちゃったし私はまだまだ子供でした",
      "startTime": 88.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 94.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんが俺に腹を立てるのは当然だ\nすぐに気持ちを切り替えられないのも仕方ないさ",
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でもアイドルとしてステージに立ったら\nみんなを楽しませることに集中してほしいんだ",
      "startTime": 104.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 107.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n応援してくれるみんなのために全力で歌います",
      "startTime": 109.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 113.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが笑顔になるような\n幸せいっぱいのクリスマスライブにしてみせます！",
      "startTime": 115.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "緊張は解けたみたいだな\nそろそろ出番だ、準備はいいか？",
      "startTime": 121.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n私達のクリスマスライブ、観ていて下さい！",
      "startTime": 126.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5500,
          "startTime": 132.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "みなさ～ん！\n今日は寒い中、来てくれてありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 134.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13047.82295230001,
          "startTime": 147.114489619
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 26963.3333333,
          "startTime": 161.03
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 37099.99999999999,
          "startTime": 171.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスイブは大切な人と過ごす日です\nそんな大切な日に私達に会いに来てくれてありがとう",
      "startTime": 142.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスをみなさんと過ごせるのが\n凄く嬉しいです……",
      "startTime": 150.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんが私のサンタクロースです！\nみなさんの笑顔が最高のクリスマスプレゼントです！",
      "startTime": 156.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "だから私からは、聖なる夜に感謝を込めて\n素敵なひとときをお届けします",
      "startTime": 165.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんに私からクリスマスプレゼント！\n今夜は楽しい思い出を沢山持って帰って下さいね！",
      "startTime": 172.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様\nトリエルらしい素敵なクリスマスライブだったよ",
      "startTime": 180.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
